name: Creature I
description:
Creature I, by Plástica · (Creature series I/III)










Plástica is an underground Galician artist. Her work moves around the human mind and body in conjunction with nature and the universe. She has received huge appraisal among the electronic music scene and has worked with world-renowned music labels. 


This is the Genesis of my curated projects. Unique and exclusive artwork from Spanish artists.
